Package org.pepstock.charba.client.annotation

Class AbstractAnnotation

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.pepstock.charba.client.commons.NativeObjectContainer
      • org.pepstock.charba.client.commons.AbstractNode
        • org.pepstock.charba.client.annotation.AbstractAnnotation
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    HasBorderOptions, HasEventsHandler, HasShadowOptions, IsDefaultsAnnotation, IsDefaultsBorderOptionsHandler, IsDefaultsEventsHandler, IsDefaultsShadowOptionsHandler
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractPointedAnnotation, BoxAnnotation, EllipseAnnotation, LineAnnotation
    public abstract class AbstractAnnotation
extends AbstractNode
implements IsDefaultsAnnotation, HasBorderOptions, HasShadowOptions, HasEventsHandler
    Base class to define an annotation in the AnnotationPlugin.ID plugin.
    It contains all commons properties to define an annotation.
    Author:
    Andrea "Stock" Stocchero
